ent-RMCChancesClaimLandingSign-name = Chance's Claim landing sign
ent-RMCChancesClaimLandingSign-desc = A large sign that reads 'Chance's Claim', with information regarding the colony written in the corner. Most of the sign is damaged from the constant wind and rain, although the writing and corporate-coloured accents seem to have been repainted.

ent-RMCHybrisaProsperaMiningSign-name = Hybrisa Prospera - Weston-Yamada Tartarus Mining - Landing Zone two sign
ent-RMCHybrisaProsperaMiningSign-desc = A large sign that reads 'WEYA - TMCC Mining - HBP - LZ - 01' The Tartarus Mining logo is adorns the sign.

ent-RMCHybrisaProsperaMedicalSign-name = Hybrisa Prospera - Emergency Medical Landing Zone one sign
ent-RMCHybrisaProsperaMedicalSign-desc = A large sign that reads 'Emergency Medical - HBP - LZ - 01'.

ent-RMCHybrisaProsperaSign-name = Hybrisa Prospera welcome sign
ent-RMCHybrisaProsperaSign-desc = A large sign that reads 'Welcome to Hybrisa Prospera', The Weston Yamada 'Wings' and logo adorn the sign, as well as some information about the colony.

ent-RMCFortBicepSign-name = Fort Bicep sign
ent-RMCFortBicepSign-desc = A large sign that reads 'Fort Bicep, T-COMMS'.

ent-RMCNewVaraderoSign-name = New Varadero landing sign
ent-RMCNewVaraderoSign-desc = A large sign that reads 'New Varadero'. Its always sunny here!

ent-RMCSorokyneSign-name = Sorokyne landing sign
ent-RMCSorokyneSign-desc = A large sign that reads 'Sorokyne - СОРОКІНО - POP. 110' The Company logo is proudly emblazoned in the corner. Don't eat the resin coated snow.

ent-RMCTrijentSign-name = Trijent landing sign
ent-RMCTrijentSign-desc = A large sign that reads 'Trijent mining col-', with the rest being obscured by what looks to be dried blood, and damage.

ent-RMCShivaIceSign-name = Shiva's Ice landing sign
ent-RMCShivaIceSign-desc = A large sign that reads 'Shiva's Ice L-nding -', bullet holes and torn metal obscure the rest of the signage.

ent-RMCPrisonSign-name = UN Prison Docking sign
ent-RMCPrisonSign-desc = A large sign that reads 'UN Prison Docking -', the rest of it is obscured by claw marks.

ent-RMCSolarisRidgeSign-name = Solaris Ridge sign
ent-RMCSolarisRidgeSign-desc = A large sign that reads 'Solaris Ridge -', the rest of it is scraped away.

ent-RMCLazarusLandingSign-name = Lazarus landing sign
ent-RMCLazarusLandingSign-desc = A large sign reading 'lazarus landing por-' the rest of it is smeared in blood.

ent-RMCBaseLandingSign-name = sign
ent-RMCBaseLandingSign-desc = A sign.

ent-RMCLazarusLandingSignFixed-name = Lazarus landing sign
ent-RMCLazarusLandingSignFixed-desc = A large sign reading 'Lazarus Landing - POP. 73'. The Company logo is emblazoned in the corner.

ent-RMCTrijentSignAlt-name = Trijent landing sign
ent-RMCTrijentSignAlt-desc = A large sign that reads 'Trijent mining colony', with half the sign written in Japanese.

ent-RMCSorokyneSignAlt-name = Sorokyne landing sign
ent-RMCSorokyneSignAlt-desc = A large sign that reads 'Sorokyne - СОРОКІНО - POP. 110' The Company logo is proudly emblazoned in the corner. Someone has crudely written 'FUCK OFF' in teal paint across the majority of the sign.

ent-RMCPortNereidCargoSign-name = Port Nereid - Weston-Yamada Cargo Depot AC-170 - Landing Zone one sign
ent-RMCPortNereidCargoSign-desc = A large sign that identifies this area as "Cargo Depot AC-170". It's clearly seen many days of rain, and jungle flora has started to creep up it.

ent-RMCPortNereidSpaceportSign-name = Port Nereid - Port Nereid International Spaceport - Landing Zone two sign
ent-RMCPortNereidSpaceportSign-desc = A large sign that reads 'Port Nereid Spaceport". Under the blue light, you can read some incredibly mundane information about the colony, above a sweeping graphic of what appears to be a stylized spaceship. Although the sign has some vine growing on it, it's clear it's been repainted many times, keeping it clean and sleek.

